For Ubuntu 18.4 (64bit), just use apt intall the toolchain:

Reference: https://www.beyondlogic.org/compiling-u-boot-with-device-tree-support-for-the-raspberry-pi/

###
apt install gcc-aarch64-linux-gnu
make CROSS_COMPILE=aarch64-linux-gnu- rpi_3_defconfig
make CROSS_COMPILE=aarch64-linux-gnu- u-boot.bin
